  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Modernization of Classroom Computer Equipment</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Modernization of Classroom Computer Equipment</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Ide o moderniz&#xE1;ciu po&#x10D;&#xED;ta&#x10D;ovej u&#x10D;ebne jedinej &#x161;koly svojho druhu na Ukrajine, poskytuje vzdel&#xE1;vanie v slovenskom jazyku. Z prostriedkov mikrograntu &#x161;kola pl&#xE1;nuje zak&#xFA;pi&#x165; 15 ks stoln&#xFD;ch po&#x10D;&#xED;ta&#x10D;ov a 15 ks LCD monitorov, kl&#xE1;vesnice, my&#x161;i, sie&#x165;ov&#xE9; komponenty (k&#xE1;ble, z&#xE1;suvky, switch), interakt&#xED;vnu tabu&#x13E;u a projektor, in&#x161;tal&#xE1;ciu po&#x10D;&#xED;ta&#x10D;ovej siete a ostatn&#xE9;ho programov&#xE9;ho vybavenia. Z prostriedkov mikrograntu pl&#xE1;nuje &#x161;kola vybavi&#x165; multimedi&#xE1;lnou technikou aj jednu u&#x10D;eb&#x148;u pre druh&#xFD; stupe&#x148; Z&#x160; (notebook + projektor).</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">It is a modernization of the computer room of the only school of its kind in Ukraine, it provides education in the Slovak language. From the microgrant&apos;s resources, the school plans to purchase 15 desktop computers and 15 LCD monitors, keyboards, mice, network components (cables, sockets, switches), an interactive whiteboard and projector, and the installation of a computer network and other software. From the resources of the microgrant, the school also plans to equip one classroom for the second stage of primary school (notebook + projector) with multimedia technology.</narrative>
  </description>
